  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/00b2d4122a4cd71194f55d054f01c2f3.poster.avif?t=1770368237\" width=550 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/00b2d4122a4cd71194f55d054f01c2f3.webm?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/00b2d4122a4cd71194f55d054f01c2f3.mp4?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>『Who's Next?』 is an online social deduction tag game for 4 to 10 players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Investigate and chase at the same time, survive until the end, and become the ultimate winner!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find your soul and identify the one you need to eliminate!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/6272a238a4cb9a2f4052a7ee4b5634a5.poster.avif?t=1770368237\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/6272a238a4cb9a2f4052a7ee4b5634a5.webm?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/6272a238a4cb9a2f4052a7ee4b5634a5.mp4?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All players are connected in a linear tag-like chain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/18885ddd96d021343ed7aa43e1caadfe.avif?t=1770368237\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras_big/18885ddd96d021343ed7aa43e1caadfe.avif?t=1770368237 width=800 height=545 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the beginning, you won’t know who your target is.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game, gather information, engage in conversations, and deduce who your target is.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gather clues by completing tasks</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/19089b5c74c381eb3d9cc537b4dee3c7.poster.avif?t=1770368237\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/19089b5c74c381eb3d9cc537b4dee3c7.webm?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/19089b5c74c381eb3d9cc537b4dee3c7.mp4?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discussion phase</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/6500ac6ab05472eeae7fbb6fd54d2778.poster.avif?t=1770368237\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/6500ac6ab05472eeae7fbb6fd54d2778.webm?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/6500ac6ab05472eeae7fbb6fd54d2778.mp4?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you've identified your target, you can attempt to eliminate them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>But be careful!! Attacking the wrong target will backfire and turn against you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/7d5090b7e7f049dc6d10186b08c8f94c.poster.avif?t=1770368237\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/7d5090b7e7f049dc6d10186b08c8f94c.webm?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/7d5090b7e7f049dc6d10186b08c8f94c.mp4?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and eliminate your target to become the last one standing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/89c644e332c1f0483f75e08a7c0e91c1.poster.avif?t=1770368237\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/89c644e332c1f0483f75e08a7c0e91c1.webm?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/89c644e332c1f0483f75e08a7c0e91c1.mp4?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Korean-inspired, cartoon-style art design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fearful background with goofy and adorable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 customizable game options</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/b376937413f3e0593714fce3564d2cf8.poster.avif?t=1770368237\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/b376937413f3e0593714fce3564d2cf8.webm?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/b376937413f3e0593714fce3564d2cf8.mp4?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real-time voice chat support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple game modes and maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse cross-platform play - PC available / Mac, iOS, Android => Coming in 2025/Q2!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Animated, expressive character skins!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regular updates with new content</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/88f17af573d0389f277dc3557564b967.poster.avif?t=1770368237\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/88f17af573d0389f277dc3557564b967.webm?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891940/extras/88f17af573d0389f277dc3557564b967.mp4?t=1770368237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Sinners of the afterlife!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Hurry and kill each other for a chance at reincarnation!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
